2.0.0
    - Briefer and clearer variable naming guidelines.
    - Improve reliability and consistency of form element styles
    - [Breaking] Variables stylesheet is now a separate import
    - [Breaking] Base styles renamed from _vellum.scss to _base.scss
    - [Breaking] Many variables removed or renamed:
        `$sans-serif`: removed; use $font-family
        `$serif`: removed
        `$leading-ratio`: removed; use $line-height or calculate inline
        `$disabled-color`: removed
        `$background-color`: removed
        `$v-space` and `$h-space`: removed, were deprecated; use $unit by default
        `$forms-border-color`: removed; use $border-color by default
        `$forms-input-color`: renamed → $input-background-color
        `$forms-active-border-color`: removed
        `$forms-focus-border-color`: renamed → $focus-color
        `$forms-border-radius`: removed; use $border-radius by default
        `$forms-font-size`: removed; use $font-size by default
        `$forms-font-family`: removed; use $font-family by default
        `$forms-checked-background`: removed
        `$forms-disabled-color`: renamed → $disabled-input-color
        `$forms-disabled-background`: renamed → $disabled-input-background-color
        `$forms-placeholder-color`: removed
    - New variables:
        `$tap-size`
        `$horizontal-input-padding`
        `$vertical-input-padding`
        `$input-padding`

1.1.1
    - Text indent removed from `select` element
    - Disabled form styles added
    - `$v-space` and `$h-space` replaced with `$unit`
    - `$unit` value is 10px
    - Grey-10, -20, -30, -40, -50 variables replaced with Neutral-30, -40, -50, -60, -70 variables
    - `$grey-gradient` renamed to `$neutral-gradient`
    - `*.css.map` added to ignore list
    - `/templates` folder renamed to `/almanac`
    - `Readme` updated

1.0.0
    - Initial Vellum release
